---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About | Tsatsin Blog"
  description="About this blog and what gets published here."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
    <h1>Why this blog exists</h1>
    <p>
      This site is intentionally small: short posts, clear writing, and practical ideas. No noise,
      just useful notes.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="about-panel">
    <h2>What to expect</h2>
    <p>
      You will find writeups on engineering trade-offs, architecture choices, and lessons from
      shipping real products.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
